CRM Fields to Track at Each Stage
Category	Fields
Lead Info	Name, Company, Email, Phone
Qualification	Budget, Authority, Need, Timeline
Sales Activity	Calls, Emails, Meetings
Opportunity	Deal Value, Probability, Expected Close Date
Proposal	Proposal Date, Quote Amount
Closing	Won/Lost Reason
Customer Success	Onboarding Status, Renewal Date, NPS
